-- Violence in Syria Has Risen to Level of War Crime, El-Arabi Says
-- B y   T a r e k   E l - T a b l a w y
-- 2012-07-29T14:39:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-29/violence-in-syria-has-risen-to-level-of-war-crime-el-arabi-says.html
Arab League chief Nabil el-Arabi
said that what is taking place in Syria, and in the city of
Aleppo, rises to the level of  war crimes , the state-run Middle
East News Agency reported.  El-Arabi said he backed calls by the Syrian opposition for
an emergency meeting of the United Nations Security Council,
adding that what was important was “we come out with”
something from such a meeting.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tarek El-Tablawy in Cairo at 
 teltablawy@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
